\c 34
\s Kufa nekuvigwa kwaMozisi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Mozisi wakakwira kubva pamapani ekwaMoabhu achienda kugomo reNebho, panhongonya yePisiga pakatarisana neJeriko. Jehovha ndokumutaridza nyika yese yeGiriyadhi, kusvika kuDhani,
\v 2 neNafutari yese, nenyika yaEfuremu, naManase, nenyika yese yaJudha kusvika pagungwa rekupedzisira;
\v 3 nechamhembe, neBani remupata weJeriko, guta remichindwe kusvika Zoari.
\v 4 Zvino Jehovha akati kwaari: Iyi inyika yandakapikira Abhurahama, Isaka, naJakove ndichiti: Ndichaipa kumbeu yako; ndakuonesa nemeso ako, asi haungayambukiriko.
\p
\v 5 Zvino Mozisi muranda waJehovha wakafirapo panyika yaMoabhu, sezvakataurwa naJehovha.
\v 6 Akamuviga pamupata panyika yaMoabhu, pakatarisana neBheti-Peori, asi hapana munhu unoziva rinda rake kusvikira nhasi.
\p
\v 7 Zvino Mozisi wakange ari wemakore ane zana namakumi maviri pakufa kwake; meso ake akange achigere kuonera madzerere, nesimba rake rakange richigere kuderera.
\p
\v 8 Vana vaIsraeri vakachema Mozisi pamapani okwaMoabhu mazuva ana makumi matatu; naizvozvo mazuva avakachema pakuchema Mozisi akapera.
\p
\v 9 Zvino Joshua, mwanakomana waNuni, wakange azere nomweya wokuchenjera; nokuti Mozisi wakange aisa maoko ake pamusoro pake; vana vaIsraeri vakamuteerera, vakaita sezvakarairwa Mozisi naJehovha.
\p
\v 10 Hakuna kuzomukazve muporofita pakati paIsraeri wakafanana naMozisi, wakange achizikanwa naJehovha, zviso zvakatarisana;
\v 11 pazviratidzo zvese nezvishamiso, paakatumwa naJehovha kundozviita panyika yeEgipita, kuna Farao, nokuvaranda vake vese, nokunyika yake yese;
\v 12 napazvese zvakaitwa noruoko rwake rune simba, napakutyisa kukuru kwese, kwakaitwa naMozisi VaIsraeri vese vachizviona.
